data.description: Brick home nestled in a cul-de-sac in Crystal Hills offering approximately 1600 sq ft of living space. This home provides 3 bedrooms, 1 3/4 bath and a 2 car garage. The living room features a vaulted ceiling and gas log fireplace with a brick mantle. Spacious dining area will accommodate a large table. All flooring (except the primary bedroom) has been replaced with ceramic tile, new paint in the interior and new stainless appliances within the last 2 years. The inground swimming pool liner, sand filter and tarp have all been replaced as well as the roof and guttering. Close to restaurants, shopping and Ft. Sill. Call listing agent Rachael Jones for more information 816-838-7687.
